Package.json
> Entry point to the app
> Contains metadata (name,version,description)
> Contains Scripts(start,build,test)
> Packages we are using for the app


/////Step to generate package.json////
* NodeJs must be install in laptop
> open cmd/terminal and go inside folder
> npm init
> Answer all questions
> type "yes"